text: Austin O'Connor and Balham Houdini at Military Boekelo 2013 Austin O'Connor (born 10 December 1974) is an Irish equestrian.FEI Biographies: Austin O'Connor He participated at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. He competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics in Beijing, where he placed 8th in team eventing with the Irish team.
